text.section:
This section applies to the following individuals:
An active duty member of the United States armed forces;
The spouse of an active duty member of the United States armed forces;
A financially dependent child of an active duty member of the United States armed forces;
An honorably discharged veteran of the United States armed forces; or
A member of the National Guard as defined in § 13-405(a)(3) of the Public Safety Article.
